reviewText:
Tape is a 30 minute EP recording put out in 1990 by the dying AWA promotion to try to mine a few dollars from the Hulkamania
craze.
 Tape is hosted by a young Eric Bischoff and features the following matches:
Hulk/Andre the Giant vs. Bobby Heenan Family (Patera, Duncum, Heenan and Bockwinkel).
Hulk vs. Bockwinkel
Several Hulk/Andre and Heenan Family promos.
Recommended-- (just wish it had been recorded in the SP format).
